Version: Deno 2.2.3

When using RSA PSS padding with crypto.sign() in Deno, it throws an error while the same code works fine in Node.js.

### Repro

```
import crypto from "node:crypto";

function sign(key: string, data: Uint8Array, saltLength: number) {
  return crypto
    .createSign("sha256")
    .update(data)
